{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-entry-js","path":"/notes/py/socket/create_server","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"socket.create_server"},"html":"<h3><code class=\"language-text\">socket.create_server(addr, family=AF_INET)</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Creates a TCP service that is bound to <code class=\"language-text\">address</code></li>\n<li>This address takes the form of <code class=\"language-text\">(host, port)</code></li>\n<li>The functions returns a socket object</li>\n<li>This function is typically used for testing with servers</li>\n<li>The address family is <code class=\"language-text\">AF_INET</code> by default</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Example of <code class=\"language-text\">create_server</code></h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> socket\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> addr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">8080</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>             <span class=\"token comment\"># accept all interfaces</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> s <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> socket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>create_server<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>addr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># listen on port 8080</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>References</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://index-of.co.uk/Python/Python%20Essential%20Reference,%20Fourth%20Edition.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Python Essential Reference</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.python.org/3/library/socket.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Documentation for socket API</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"py/socket/create_server","previousSlug":"py/socket/create_connection","nextSlug":"py/socket/getaddrinfo","previousTitle":"socket.create_connection","nextTitle":"socket.getaddrinfo"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}